headline: ROSS STORES, INC. ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER AND FISCAL 2025 EARNINGS RELEASE AND CONFERENCE CALL
summary: Ross Stores, Inc. (Nasdaq: ROST) plans to release its fourth quarter and fiscal 2025 earnings results on Tuesday, March 3, 2026 at approximately 4:00 p.m. Eastern time.

headline: UBS Maintains Neutral on Ross Stores, Raises Price Target to $199
summary: UBS  analyst Jay Sole   maintains Ross Stores (NASDAQ:ROST) with a Neutral and raises the price target from $181 to $199.
